How to use the application:
For adding a marker, simply click on the preferred size and then click on the "Place Marker" button.
Then choose a location and simply left-click.
When in minimized mode, right-click on the Virtual Marker icon in the taskbar and click on the preferred size.

For removing a marker, right click on the taskbar icon and then hover the cursor over the mode you currently have open and click on "Remove Marker"
[OR] if you want to close all the ones open, simply right click on the taskbar icon and then click on "Remove all Markers"

